---
layout: default.njk
---

<section id="top-section">
  <img
    id="uvm-bg"
    src="/assets/campus-background.jpg"
    alt="Drone view of UVM's central campus."
  />

  <div class="inner-section hero-text">
    <!-- <img src="/assets/campus-background.jpg"
            alt=""> -->
    <div class="style-bar"></div>
    <h2 class="target-identity">Hey Catamounts,</h2>
    <h3 class="call-to-action">
      Think. Talk.
      <span class="action-emphasis">Vote.</span>
    </h3>
    <p>It's never too early to be ready â€” let's get to the ballot box.</p>
    <a href="/turbovote" class="cta-btn">Make a Plan</a>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="inner-section">
    <h2
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      Non-Partisan
    </h2>
    <p
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      We're a club committed to improving the student-voter experience.
      <a class="link" href="#sign-up">Get involved!</a>
    </p>

    <img
      src="assets/images/lizAndAidan.webp"
      alt="UVM Votes members carving pumpkins."
    />
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="inner-section" id="the-issue">
    <h2
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      The Problem
    </h2>

    <div class="non-flex-wrapper">
      <figure class="highcharts-figure">
        <div id="container"></div>
      </figure>
    </div>
    <p
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      From
      <a class="link" href="/campus-reports" target="_blank"
        >our campus report</a
      >, we know UVM students vote at a lower rate than other schools, and
      college students vote at a low rate in general. That's not good for
      student representation, the values of higher ed, or the diversity of our
      democracy at large.
    </p>

    <p
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      We're seeing this for a few reasons. To name a few, newly eligible voters
      are still learning the voting process, some states intimidate student
      voters (implying they aren't eligible to vote where they live), and the
      conversation about democracy's importance across academic disciplines is
      waning.
    </p>

    <p
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
      class="bold"
    >
      We can help.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="fun-list">
  <div class="inner-section">
    <h2
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      The Solutions
    </h2>
    <p
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      Institutionalize voting! The university can access thousands of students
      in a unique way which clubs alone simply aren't able. Carving out pathways
      with the administration alleviates the organizing strain of beginning
      fresh each election cycle, and could mean more time spent discussing the
      issues with less time worrying about voting infrastructure.
    </p>
    <ul class="z-index-raised">
      <li>
        Make Election Day a campus holiday, consistent with
        <a
          class="link"
          target="_blank"
          href="https://www.to2v.org/student-body-president-letter"
          >the letter the SGA signed</a
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        Have UVM
        <a
          class="link"
          target="_blank"
          href="/blog/institutional-tools-for-student-voter-outreach-07-2021/"
          >text every student a link to</a
        >
        Turbo Vote.
      </li>
      <li>Integrate voter registration into student orientation days.</li>
      <li>
        Add a polling site for the
        <a
          class="link"
          target="_blank"
          href="https://vtcynic.com/news/a-gerrymandered-student-ward-how-burlingtons-ward-8-got-its-shape/"
          >gerrymandered student ward</a
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        Promote voter registration in clubs, fraternities, and sororities.
      </li>
      <li>
        Bring engaging events to campus like
        <a
          class="link"
          target="_blank"
          href="/blog/pumpkins-for-democracy-05-2021/"
          >Pumpkins for Democracy</a
        >
        or chalking sidewalks.
      </li>
      <li>
        Research how to
        <a
          class="link"
          target="_blank"
          href="/blog/establishing-an-sga-research-committee-06-2021/"
          >make SGA elections more competitive</a
        >.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div id="sign-up">
      <form name="Role request" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
        <h3>Get Involved!</h3>
        <div class="user-box">
          <input type="text" name="name" required="" />
          <label>Email:</label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-bottom">
          <div class="quick-fix-thanks">
            <label>
              <input
                type="radio"
                name="interest"
                value="Volunteer"
                checked="checked"
              />
              Volunteer
            </label>
            <label>
              <input type="radio" name="interest" value="Organize" />
              Organize
            </label>
          </div>
          <button class="link-btn bg-blue" type="submit">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="inner-section beneath-intersecting-elm">
    <h2
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      Supporting Every State
    </h2>
    <p>
      UVM students hail from around the country, and we've got the resources to
      support everyone. Select your state for more information.
    </p>
    {% include 'statesMap.njk' %}
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="inner-section" id="contact-us">
    <h2
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      Contact
    </h2>
    <p
      data-sal="slide-right"
      data-sal-duration="1000"
      data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
    >
      We're going into this work wide-eyed and
      <em>love</em>
      talking about it, so don't hesitate to reach out!
    </p>

    <div class="grid-container" id="contact">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <img
          src="assets/images/profile-pics/headshot.webp"
          class="profile-pic"
          alt="Profile picture of James"
        />
        <div class="title">President</div>
      </div>
      <a class="email" href="mailto:james@uvm.vote">James</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
